Method 1
===============================
step 1 : open cmd/terminal/
step 2: Download 
step 3: go to the folder which has the above file hello-n-ver.pem
step 4: Run the following command 
        chmod 400 hello-n-ver.pem
        ssh -i "hello-n-ver.pem" root@ec2-54-173-214-92.compute-1.amazonaws.com
